{"tid":923963,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"以前讀書果陣我同個同學去睇風起了","createTime":"2018-12-01T16:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T20:22:25.000Z","uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5029fc990393484b83c870f27c781dc25bf3732b","tid":923963,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"以前讀書果陣我同個同學去睇風起了，睇完風起了之後佢話頭暈，然後我call白車送佢去醫院，醫生話可能套戲太刺激，令佢有輕微腦震盪，我問醫生佢重有冇得救，醫生話佢已經盡左力架喇。<br />\n出左院之後，佢話自己係美國隊長，然後佢成日拎D垃圾桶蓋周圍飛，我叫佢唔好係到發癲，佢話 I can do this all day，佢又成日叫我做巴奇，我就叫佢收皮。<br />\n有一次佢見到訓導主任，然後佢大叫&quot;紅骷顱，我屌你老母啊！！！&quot;之後佢拎個垃圾桶蓋飛中咗訓導主任個頭，然後佢比人記左個大過，自從果次之後佢就冇再睇宮崎駿嘅電影。"},{"pid":"90bea7321346ec2cffc41af76dc16e8ef29e3cf7","tid":923963,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41ea4dfaa9419ef2944fc41b2510a95b5032fd7","tid":923963,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:55:33.000Z","msg":"Ok la"},{"pid":"ef1a11ce5d5ad3dc277457ed4c3f4da8eb581f56","tid":923963,"uid":52683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"笑咗 5/10啦"},{"pid":"d33be31c01ab7d2e8c8bb66962ecb27fa3d452a5","tid":923963,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1a11ce5d5ad3dc277457ed4c3f4da8eb581f56","tid":923963,"uid":52683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"笑咗 5/10啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef86383481493bfc635e011832fb2a2059ef702","tid":923963,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d33be31c01ab7d2e8c8bb66962ecb27fa3d452a5","tid":923963,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1a11ce5d5ad3dc277457ed4c3f4da8eb581f56","tid":923963,"uid":52683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-